- The deletePrintShopReview method is annotated with @RequestMapping(value = "/printshops/{printShopId}/reviews/{reviewId}", method = RequestMethod.DELETE). - There are no other mappings in this controller method for the same path using GET, POST, PUT, PATCH, HEAD, OPTIONS, TRACE, or any other HTTP method. Therefore, only DELETE is acceptable for this endpoint.
- Since the code does not provide a mapping for HEAD (or any of the other methods) on this path, those methods are not supported by this endpoint according to the code.
